						<summary>

						<p>On the tiers of the entrance to the Saṅgamēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>Nallasiddhi, A.D. 1203.</p>						

						<p>Dated Śaka 11[2]6, <hi rend="italic">Rudhirōdgārin, Āśvija.</hi> The cyclic year corresponds to Śaka. 1125 and Āśvija corresponds to 8th September-6th October of 1203 A.D.</p>						

						<p>Registers a gift of a perpetual lamp by Nallagāmaka, the queen of Nallasiddhirāju, to the god Saṅgāmudēva.</p>						

						</summary>
