<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrīmatu sakavaruṣamulu 11<unclear>2</unclear>6 rudhirōdgāri saṁvatsaramu Āsvi(śvī) 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ja māsamunaṁdu nallasiddhirājudēvulu nallagāmaka viri 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>yūri saṁgāmu dēvaraku Akhaṁḍadīpamu Ācaṁdra sthāyi 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>gā beṭṭenu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> I (Ī) dharmmuvu māhēśvara rakṣamaṁgaḷamahā śrī [<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>] 
<lb n="5"/>śrīmatu nallakētamaraḍḍi koḍuku dāmana peṭṭina saṁdadīpa (saṁdhyādīpamu) <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
</p>

